rows.label: tev056191_MSG0001
rows.name:
Meh-meh! Great friend empowered by spirits!
Now listen to what Divine Nopopon has to say...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0002
rows.name:
Divine Nopopon was nearly wiped from existence by
strange fullbelly-gecko-like creature.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0003
rows.name:
It told Divine Nopopon that there no such thing as
ghosts...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0004
rows.name:
Then it use crackly electric weapon to stun and kidnap
Divine Nopopon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0005
rows.name:
Evil fullbelly gecko wanted to conduct nasty experiment
to see what happen as Divine Nopopon subjected to
voltage. Thankfully, Divine Nopopon manage to escape.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0006
rows.name:
But fullbelly gecko made mistake and accidentally told
Divine Nopopon name... It is actually Lulladu![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0007
rows.name:
Fullbelly gecko must be punished! It must learn price of
messing with eternal being like Divine Nopopon! Meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0008
rows.name:
So, great friend empowered by spirits...
Tell Divine Nopopon weakness of fullbelly-gecko-like
creature![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_JNK0010
rows.name: Suggest Pizza[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Nopopon that Ma-non hate pizza.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_JNK0020
rows.name: Suggest Voltant[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Nopopon that Ma-non hate voltant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0009
rows.name:
Hmm... So friend thinks evil creature will cower in fear
if presented with this...pizza?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0010
rows.name:
So be it! Divine Nopopon will send vast quantities of
pizza to foolish creature![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0011
rows.name:
Hear me, O spirits! Divine Nopopon commands you
to rain pizza down on sinner known as Lulladu![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0012
rows.name: With toppings of heaven, Divine Nopopon SMITES thee![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0013
rows.name:
Hmm... So friend says that evil creature has weakness
to this...voltant?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0014
rows.name:
Very well! Nopopon will send vast quantities of voltant
to foolish critter![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0015
rows.name:
Hear me, O spirits! Divine Nopopon commands you
to blow sinner known as Lulladu away in great
voltant vortex![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056191_MSG0016
rows.name: By power of heaven, Divine Nopopon SMITES thee![ST:wait ]
